{"tid":150843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<月經> 年輕是原罪廢老幾時先死哂","createTime":"2017-03-10T11:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T16:03:47.000Z","uid":61766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3aa35ff18abecea8f7a59e5830005b9024ee4db","tid":150843,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾港鐵洗錢叫人唔好揹住背包搭港鐵不如洗錢教育下班廢老<br />\n<br />\n我去旺角，係調景嶺上車，個批鬥座無人坐我就坐左落去<br />\n<br />\n坐左兩個站，有個白頭髮但勁好中氣既阿婆問我<br />\n婆：小姐，你個位可唔可以比我坐？<br />\n我：好呀（秒彈起身）<br />\n婆（坐左落去）：你坐錯位喎<br />\n我：下？個位有寫你名架？<br />\n婆（呆左）：我話你坐錯位呀<br />\n我：下？個位有寫你名架？<br />\n婆：個位你唔應該坐架<br />\n我：你話要坐我已經有讓比你啦<br />\n跟住佢收左嗲<br />\n<br />\n坐多兩個站，有個呀媽帶住件六七歲既細路上車<br />\n婆：你地邊個站落呀，比你地坐呀<br />\n媽：旺角，不過唔洗啦，比佢企下啦<br />\n婆：得啦我下個站落，拿呢個位就係你架啦！<br />\n<br />\n究竟乜撚野邏輯，我比既車費又多d，坐下個位又要比人屌，年輕人真係咪撚學人攰，已經唔係唔讓，都要屌，阿婆，願你百病纏身，長命百歲"},{"pid":"a6158699483c1b5f21f513c91011a54e223fbc67","tid":150843,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"廢老讓座比佢 都咁撚多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51be039ce451af5d7780dce008180d65a4cc267d","tid":150843,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb0cf488383b0928fe685e86c23f23011429cee","tid":150843,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"比我就直接話唔得 屌那星家陣老奉讓比你？"},{"pid":"4d8cc755e3ad7e4a15d44ff0d61921118440751b","tid":150843,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老讓座比佢 都咁撚多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要驚撚死我會再搶黎坐屌佢祖宗十八代"},{"pid":"773703cd5966411a10e71ae548d9c30f27656071","tid":150843,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b246301ca9ede9019a266c99e6fd6ccecb8ece77","tid":150843,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"仲讓畀佢係你on9"},{"pid":"5d7ddbf6e4f9140708eaa99f1beaa240c528a96b","tid":150843,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲讓畀佢係你on9</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n下佢都坐左係度唔通我叫佢讓返比我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}